snippet.title: FilmiBeat
snippet.description:
Filmibeat.com is the No.1 multi-language entertainment portal for all the crazy movie-buffs who want daily updates on Movies and the Television industry. It is one of India's most-reputed movie info portals that keeps you updated with all the daily gossip, movie review, box office report, celebrity interviews, videos, photos from glamorous world of Cinema and TV

This channel having 3rd party videos shared by PR/Media/Production houses and Advertising Agencies. Videos uploaded on this channel only after giving due credits to the team that has worked on it

Filmibeat is a part of Greynium Information Technologies Pvt. which runs Oneindia.com India’s # 1 language portal. It caters to a wide variety of tastes of Indian Internet users by delivering content, community, entertainment and commerce in 8 languages: English, Gujarati, Hindi, Kannada, Malayalam, Tamil, Telugu and Bengali.

In case of objection to any video content uploaded on this channel, please write to inquiries@oneindia.co.in
